snippet.title: Amber Heard: 'I Don't Want To Be A Celebrity' - Splash News | Splash News TV | Splash News TV
snippet.description:
The Rum Diary actress made it clear she wants to be taken seriously in the film industry. She said, "I want to be an artist. I don't want to be a celebrity." She went on to say you won't see photos of her at nightclubs and bars... she's not going to change just because she's in the public eye.
